to Virginia529 accounts  up to  4 000 per account  from their individual state taxable income  Open or add to an existing account by December 31  2015 to use the deduction for the 2015 tax year  Annual prePAID enrollment The 2015 16 enrollment period for the Virginia529 prePAID tuition program opened December 1  2015 and continues through March 31  2016  FAQs  tutorials  and a convenient prePAID calculator are available at Virginia529 com prepaid  Free workshops and materials Virginia529 comes to you with free workshops  program guides and brochures  Invite them to your next benefit fair or employee orientation or host a college savings information session  For more information  visit Virginia529 com  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 